hadiths[82]{hadithnumber,text}:
3888,Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jab to kisi mazdoor sey mazduri karana chahey (kisi shakhs ko naukar aur mulaazim rakhey) to usey uski ujrat saaf bata dey.
3889,"Hazrat Hasan Basri sey marwi hai, unhoney napasand farmaya ke kisi shakhs ko uski ujrat aur mazduri bataey baghair mazdoor rakha jaey."
3890,Hazrat Hammad bin Abi Suleman (Alaihissalam) sey puchha gaya : kya kisi ko naukar rakha ja sakta hai is shart par ke usey khana milega? farmaya : nahin magar ye ke usey batla diya jaey.
3891,"Hazrat Hammad aur Hazrat Qatada sey manqul hai ke eik shakhs dusrey sey kahe ke main tujh sey Makka tak key liye sawari itney kiraaye par leta hun, agar pura mahina ya itni muddat (jis ki wo sarahat kerey) safar mein raha to tujhey itney rupey mazeed dunga. to un dono buzurgon ney is mein koi harj nahin samjha. albatta unhoney is baat ko napasand kiya hai ke wo kahe : main tujh sey ye sawari itney kiraaye par leta hun aur agar main eik maah sey ziyada safar main raha to tujhey itna kiraaya kam dunga."
3892,"Hazrat ibne Juraij ney kaha : mainey Hazrat Ata sey puchha : main eik ghulam ko eik saal key liye sirf khurak ki shart par aur eik saal key liye itni (moayan) raqam par naukar rakhta hun (kya ye jayez hai?) unhoney farmaya : koi harj nahin, aur naukar rakhtey waqt jo shart laga ley, wo durust hai. (mainey kaha :) agar main usey naukar rakhun jabkey saal ka kuchh hissa guzar chuka ho? wo farmaney lagey : to guzishta dino ka hisab nahin kerega."
3893,Hazrat Usaid bin Zuher (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke main apni qom banu Harisa ki taraf gaya aur unhen kaha : aey banu Harisa ! tum par eik naee musibat nazil ho gaee hai. wo kehney lagey : wo kya? mainey kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zamin kiraaey par deney sey rok diya hai. hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum moayan (taishuda) ghalley key iwaz bataai par dey saktey hain? aap ney farmaya : nahin. mainey kaha : hum moayan (taishuda) todi key iwaz zamin kiraaye par detey they? aap ney farmaya : nahin. (mainey arz ki : ) hum pani waley naalon key qarib ugney wali fasal key iwaz zamin bataai par detey they? aap ney farmaya : nahin. khud ka kaasht karo ya apney (deeni) bhai ko bator Atiya (kuchh muddat key liye) dey do. Hazrat Mujahid ney Hazrat Raafey bin Usaid ki mukhalifat ki hai.
3894,Hazrat Usaid bin Zuher (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamarey paas Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tumhen tihai ya chothai par zamin bator bataai deney sey rok diya hai. isi tarah aap ney mazaabna sey bhi rok diya hai. aur mazaabna ye hai ke darkht key ooper lagey huye phal ko khushk khajuron ki moayan miqdaar key iwaz kharid ya bechaa jaey.
3895,"Hazrat Usaid bin Zuher (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein aisey kaam sey mana farma diya hai jo hamarey liye mufeed tha. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki itaat hi tumharey liye behtar hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tumhen mazaariat (bataai) sey rok diya hai aur aap ney farmaya hai : jis shakhs key paas faaltu zamin hai, wo kisi ko bator Atiya dey dey ya usey aisey hi rehney dey. isi tarah aap ney mazaabna sey bhi mana farma diya hai. aur mazaabna ye hai ke eik aadmi key paas bahut sey khajoor key darkht hon. koi doosra shakhs aaye aur darakhton par lagi hui khajuron ko moayan (taishuda) khushk khajuron key iwaz khareedey."
3896,"Hazrat Usaid bin Zuher (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur kaha … lekin main (mumaaniat (manahi) ki wajeh) nahin samajh saka … Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tumhen aisey kaam sey mana farma diya hai jo tumharey liye mufeed tha. lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki itaat us mufeed kaam sey tumharey liye badarjaha behtar hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tumhen haql sey rok diya hai. aur haql sey murad zamin ko tihai ya chothai hissey key iwaz bataai par dena hai, lihaza jis shakhs key paas faaltu zamin hai, jiski usey zarurat nahin to wo apney kisi (musalman gharib) bhai ko dey dey ya phir chhod dey. isi tarah aap ney mazaabna sey bhi mana farmaya hai. aur mazaabna ye hai ke eik shakhs khajoor key bahut sey darakhton key paas bahut si khushk khajuren ley kar aaye aur kahe : ye itney itney (yani moayan (taishuda)) wasq khajuron key iwaz ley ley."
3897,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tumhen (yani badey zameendaar ansaar ko) eik aisey kaam sey rok diya hai jo hamarey liye faeyde-mand tha magar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki itaat hamarey liye har chiz sey badh kar mufeed hai. aap ney farmaya : jis shakhs key paas zamin ho, wo usey khud kaasht kerey. agar wo khud kaasht na kar sakey to apney kisi musalman bhai ko (bila-iwaz) kaasht key liye (waqti taur par) dey dey. Abdul-Kareem bin Malik ney Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman ki mukhalifat ki hai."
3898,"Hazrat Mujahid (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Taoos ka haath pakda aur unhen Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) key kisi betey key paas la khada kiya to us ney unhen apney walid key wastey sey bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zamin bataai par deney sey mana kiya hai. lekin Hazrat Taoos ney taslim na kiya. wo farmaney lagey : mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey khud suna hai, wo is mein koi harj nahin samajhtey they. ye riwayat Abu-Awaana ney Abu-Haseen sey, unhoney Mujahid sey aur Mujahid ney Abu-Raafea' sey mursal bayan ki hai."
3899,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein eik aisey kaam sey mana farma diya jo hamarey liye mufeed tha. lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka farman sar aur aakhon par (basar aur chashm taslim kiya hai). aap ney hamein mana farmaya ke hum zamin ko uski kuchh pedawar key iwaz kiraaye par den. Ibrahim bin Muhaajir ney (Abu-Haseen ki) mutaabiat (pairwi) ki hai (isi tarah Hukm aur Abdul-Malik ney bhi).
3900,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik Ansari aadmi ki zamin key paas sey guzrey. aap jantey they ke wo shakhs mohtaj hai. aap ney farmaya : ye zamin kis ki hai? us ney kaha : falan ki hai. us ney mujhey kiraaey (bataai ya thekey) par di hai. aap ney farmaya : agar wo apney is (gharib) bhai ko (waqti taur par atiye key taur par) dey deta (to kya hi khub hota). to Hazrat Raafey ansaar key paas aaye aur kehney lagey : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tumhen aisey kaam sey mana farma diya hai jo tumharey liye mufeed tha lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki itaat tumharey liye har chiz sey badh kar mufeed hai.
3901,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mazaariat sey mana farmaya hai.
3902,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur hamein aisey kaam sey mana farma diya jo hamarey liye nafa-mand tha. aap ney farmaya : jis shakhs key paas zamin ho, wo usey khud kaasht karey ya kisi bhai ko bator Atiya (kaasht key liye) dey dey, ya phir padi rehney dey."
3903,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur hamein aisey kaam sey mana farmaya jo hamarey liye mufid tha. lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka farman hi hamarey liye sab sey badh kar behtar hai. aap ney farmaya : jis shakhs key paas (faaltu) zamin ho, wo usey khud kaasht karey ya padi rehney dey ya kisi bhai ko bator waqti Atiya key dey dey. ye hadees (3904) dalalat karti hai ke Taoos ney ye hadees Hazrat Raafey sey nahin suni."
3904,"Hazrat Amr bin Dinar bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Taoos apni zamin soney chaandi (yani raqam) key iwaz thekey par dena napasand kartey they lekin tihai ya chothai pedawar key iwaz bataai par dena jayez samajhtey they. Hazrat Mujahid ney un sey kaha : Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) key betey key yahan jaiye aur un sey un ki hadees suniye. unhoney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! agar mujhey ilm hota ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney is sey mana farmaya hai to main hergiz ye kaam na karta lekin mujhey un sey badey aalim Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney to sirf ye farmaya tha : tum mein sey koi shakhs apney (musalman) bhai ko apni (faaltu) zamin bator Atiya key dey dey to ye uskey liye behtar hai, bajaey is baat key ke wo us sey muqarrara pedawar wasul kar ley. is hadees mein Ata par ikhtilaf kiya gaya hai (Ata key shagirdon ney is par ikhtilaf kiya hai aur wo is tarah ke) Abdul-Malik bin Maisraa ney (jab bayan kiya to) kaha : (an Ata an Raafey). iska zikr hum sabiqa (pichhli) hadees mein kar aaye hain. aur Abdul-Malik bin Abi Suleman (Alaihissalam) ney (jab bayan kiya to) kaha : (an Ata an Jabir)."
3905,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs key paas (faaltu) zamin ho, wo usey khud kaasht kerey. agar wo khud kaasht na kar sakta ho to apney musalman bhai ko bator waqti Atiya key dey dey. bataai ya thekey par na dey."
3906,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs key paas zamin ho, wo usey khud kaasht karey ya apney kisi bhai ko waqti taur par bator Atiya dey dey lekin usey kiraaye (bataai ya thekey) par na dey. is hadees ko ((an Ata an Jabir) sey) bayan karney mein Abdur-Rehman bin Amr Auzai ney Abdul-Malik bin Abi Suleman (Alaihissalam) ki mutaabiat (pairwi) ki hai."
3907,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke kuchh logon key paas faaltu zameenein thin. wo unhen nisf (aadhe) ya tihai ya chothai pedawar key iwaz bataai par detey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs key paas faaltu zamin ho, wo usey khud kaasht karey ya kisi Islaami bhai ko bila-moawza kaasht key liye dey dey ya phir sanbhaley rakhey. Matar bin Tahmaan ney us  (Auzai) ki muwaafiqat ki hai. (Matar ney bhi apni riwayat mein (an Ata an Jabir) kaha hai, na ke (an ibne-Abbas)."
3908,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein khutba irshad farmaya aur kaha : jis shakhs key paas (faaltu) zamin ho, wo usey khud kaasht karey ya kisi ko bila-moawza kaasht key liye dey dey. usey kiraaye par na dey."
3909,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marfooan (aap se sidhey taur par) riwayat hai ke (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney) zamin ko kiraaye par deney sey mana farmaya hai. zamin kiraaey ya thekey par deney ki mumaaniat (manahi) key masley mein Abdul-Malik bin Abdul-Azeez bin Juraij ney Matar bin Tahmaan ki muwaafiqat ki hai. (wallahu-aalam).
3910,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mukhaahira, mazaabna, muhaaqla aur kachchey phalon ki bai sey mana farmaya hai magar araayaa ki bai ho sakti hai. Yunus bin Ubaid ney ibne Juraij ki mutaabiat (pairwi) ki hai."
3911,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muhaaqla, mazaabna, mukhaahira aur majhool istisna karney sey mana farmaya hai, haan istisna malum ho to kiya ja sakta hai. Hamaam bin Yahya ki riwayat goya daleel ki tarah hai is par ke Ata ney Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan karda ye hadees nahin suni : jiski zamin ho usey chahiye ke wo khud usey kaasht kerey."
3912,"Hazrat Jabir bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs key paas (faaltu) zamin ho, wo usey khud kaasht karey ya apney kisi bhai ko bila-moawza kaasht key liye dey dey lekin usey kiraaye par na dey. muhaaqla sey mumaaniat (ki hadees) Yazid bin Naeem ney Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai."
3913,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney haql sey mana farmaya hai aur us sey murad mazaabna hai. Hisham bin abi Abdullah ney Muawiya bin Salam ki mukhalifat ki hai.
3914,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mazaabna aur mukhazra sey mana farmaya hai. aur mukhazra ye hai ke phal pakney sey qabl uski bai (bikri) ki jaey. aur mukhaahira ye hai ke darkht par lagey angooron ki bai muqarrara wazan ki munaqqaa (khushk angooron) sey ki jaey. umr bin Abu-Salma ney Yahya bin Abu-Kaseer ki mukhalifat ki hai ke unhoney (عن ابیہ an ابی ہریرۃ) kaha hai ( jabkey Yahya ney (عن ابی سلمۃ an جابر) kaha hai.)
3915,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muhaaqla aur mazaabna sey mana farmaya. Muhammad bin Amr Laisi ney Yahya bin Abu-Kaseer aur umr bin Abu-Salma ki mukhalifat ki hai. aur usey Abu-Salma key wastey sey Abu-Saeed sey riwayat kiya hai.
3916,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muhaaqla aur mazaabna sey mana farmaya. Aswad bin Ala ney in (teeno, yani Muhammad bin Amr, umr bin Abu-Salma aur Yahya bin Abu-Kaseer) ki mukhalifat ki hai. aur (us ney apni sanad mein) kaha hai : (عن ابی سلمۃ ‘ an رافع ابن خدیج)."
3917,Hazrat Raafey bin Hadeej (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muhaaqla aur mazaabna sey mana farmaya. ye riwayat Qasim bin Muhammad ney bhi Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij sey bayan ki hai.
3918,Usman bin Murra ney kaha ke mainey Qasim (bin Muhammad) sey kheti (muzarbat) key mutalliq puchha to unhoney Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muhaaqla aur mazaabna sey mana farmaya hai. Imam Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney eik dusri baar yun farmaya.
3919,Hazrat Usman bin Murra ney kaha ke mainey Hazrat Qasim sey zamin kiraaey par deney key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zamin ko kiraaey (bataaii ya thekey) par deney sey mana farmaya hai. is hadees mein Saeed bin Musaiyab par ikhtilaf kiya gaya hai.
3920,Hazrat Abu-Jafar Umer bin Yazid Khutmi sey riwayat hai ke merey chacha ney mujhey aur apney eik ghulam ko Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahmatullahi Alaih) key paas bataai key barey mein poochhney key liye bheja. to wo farmaney lagey ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) is mein koi harj nahin samajhtey they yahan tak ke unkey paas Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees pahunchi to wo un sey ja kar miley. Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) banu Harisa key yahan tashrif laye to aap ney eik khet dekha. aap ney farmaya : Zuher ki kheti kis qadr achchhi hai? logon ney kaha : ye kheti Zuher ki nahin. aap ney farmaya : kya ye Zuher ki zamin nahin ? logon ney kaha : zarur ye zamin usi ki hai magar us ney aagey kiraaey par dey rakhi hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apni kheti lo aur usey us ka kharcha wapis kar do. Hazrat Raafey ney farmaya : hamney apni kheti (fasal) ley li aur kheti karne wale ko us ka kharcha aur mehnat wapis kar di. Taariq bin Abdur-Rehman ney is riwayat ko Saeed bin Musaiyab sey riwayat kiya hai lekin raawiyon ney us hadees mein un par ikhtilaf kiya hai.
3921,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muhaaqla aur mazaabna sey mana farmaya hai. Hazrat Saeed ney farmaya : kaasht kaar teen qism key hotey hain : eik to wo jiski apni zamin hai aur wo is mein kaasht karta hai. doosra wo shakhs jisey kuchh arsey key liye zamin kaasht key liye (bator Atiya) dey di jati hai aur wo is mein kaasht karta hai. teesra wo jo zamin soney chaandi key iwaz kiraaey (thekey) par leta hai. (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya ke) Israel ney is riwayat ko Taariq sey sun kar juda kiya, chunanche us ney pehley kalam ko mursal kiya aur aakhiri kalam ( انما یزرع ثلاثۃ … ) key mutalliq kaha ke ye Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ka qol hai, hadeesey-Rasool nahin."
3922,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muhaaqla sey mana farmaya hai. Saeed ney kaha … aur aagey is (Saeed) ney isi (mazkura riwayat) ki tarah zikr kiya (yani (انما یزرع ثلاثۃ)). Sufiyan Sauri ney bhi Taariq sey ye hadees riwayat ki hai (jis tarah ke Israel ney Taariq sey riwayat ki hai).
3923,Hazrat Taariq sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab ko farmatey suna ke kaashtkaari teen qisam hi ki ho sakti hai : apni mamlooka zamin mein kaasht ki jaey. waqti atiye key taur par mili hui zamin mein kaasht ki jaey ya khaali zamin soney chaandi (yani rupey paise) key iwaz thekey par ley kar kaasht ki jaey. Zohri ney kalam awwal ko Saeed bin Musaiyab sey riwayat kiya aur us ney isey mursal bayan kiya hai.
3924,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney muhaaqla aur mazaabna sey mana farmaya hai. Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman bin Labeeba ney isey Saeed bin Musaiyab sey riwayat kiya aur unhoney kaha ke ye Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai.
3925,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein faaltu zamin rakhney waley apni zameenein pani key naalon key qarib ugney wali fasal key iwaz bataai par diya kartey they. phir (kabhi-kabhi) log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir ho kar uski baabat aapas mein ladtey jhagadtey, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney in ko is tarah bataai par deney sey mana kar diya aur farmaya : soney chaandi (rupey paise) key iwaz thekey par diya karo. Suleman (Alaihissalam) ney Raafey sey ye hadees bayan ki to kaha : (عن رجل من عمومتہ) (unkey chchaaon mein sey eik sahab sey)."
3926,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein apni zameenein pedawar ki tihai ya chothai ya muqarrara miqdaar mein ghalley key iwaz bataai par diya kartey they. eik din merey chchaon mein sey koi sahab aaye aur kehney lagey : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey aisey kaam sey rok diya hai jo hamarey liye bahut mufeed tha, jabkey Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki itaat hamarey liye har chiz sey badh kar mufeed hai. aap ney hamein zameenein pedawar key tihai ya chothai hissey ya moayan (taishuda) ghalley key iwaz bataai par deney sey mana farma diya hai. aur aap ney zamin key Malik ko hukm diya hai ke wo khud kaasht karey ya kisi (musalman bhai) ko bila-moawza kaasht key liye dey dey. aap ney bataai thekey waghera ko sakht napasand farmaya hai. Ayub ney Yala bin Hakim sey ye hadees nahin suni."
3927,"Ayub bayan kartey hain ke Yala bin Hakim ney mujhey likha ke mainey Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar sey suna, wo Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij sey hadees bayan kartey they ke Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : hum apni faaltu zameenein pedawar ki tihai ya chothai ya moayan (taishuda) ghalley key iwaz bataai par diya kartey they. Saeed ney ye riwayat Yala bin Hakim sey bayan ki hai."
3928,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein zamin bataai par diya kartey they. phir merey eik chacha aaye aur kehney lagey : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney is kaam sey rok diya hai jo hamarey liye mufeed tha. lekin Allah aur uskey Rasool ki itaat hamarey liye har chiz sey badh kar mufeed hai. hamney puchha : wo kon sa kaam hai? unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : jis shakhs key paas zamin ho, wo usey khud kaasht karey ya apney kisi bhai ko (bator tohfa) kaasht key liye dey dey aur usey pedawar key tihai ya chothai ya moayan ghalley key iwaz kiraaye par na dey. is hadees ko Hanzala bin Qais ney Hazrat Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kiya hai (aur Hanzala sey Rabeea ney riwayat kiya hai) to Rabeea par is hadees ki riwayat mein ( س key shagirdon ki taraf sey) ikhtilaf kiya gaya hai."
3929,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, kehtey hain ke mujhey merey chacha ney bayan farmaya ke hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein naalon key qarib ugney wali kheti ya mutayyan (tai-shuda) ghalla jisey zamin wala khud mustashnaa karta tha, key iwaz zamin kiraey par detey they. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein is kaam sey mana farma diya. (raawi kehta hai :) mainey Hazrat Raafey sey puchha : deenar aur dirham (rupey paise) key iwaz thekey par zamin dena kaisa hai? to Hazrat Raafey ney farmaya : soney chaandi (rupey paise) key iwaz thekey par deney mein koi harj nahin. Imam Auzai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney is (Lais) ki mukhalifat ki hai."
3930,"Hazrat Hanzala bin Qais Ansari sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey soney chaandi (rupey paise) key iwaz zamin kiraey par deney sey mutalliq puchha to unhoney farmaya : is mein koi harj nahin. asal baat ye thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein log apni zameenein naalon key sath sath aur naalon key samney ugney wali fasal key iwaz bataai par detey they. kabhi is hissey ki fasal mehfooz rehti aur dusrey hissey ki zaya ho jati. kabhi dusrey hissey ki fasal mehfooz rehti aur is hissey ki fasal zaya ho jati. us waqt zamin key kiraey ki ye shakal hi raaij (chalan mein) thi, is liye aap ney us sey mana farma diya. lekin koi aur malum aur moayan (tai-shuda) chiz (raqam) muqarrar kar li jaey jin ka koi zaamin bhi ho to koi harj nahin. Malik bin Anas ney is (Auzai) ki sanad mein muwaafiqat ki hai aur is (Auzai) key alfaz mein iski mukhalifat ki hai."
3931,"Hazrat Hanzala bin Qais sey riwayat hai, farmatey hain ke mainey Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey zamin kiraey par deney key barey mein puchha. unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zamin kiraey (bataai) par deney sey mana farmaya hai. mainey kaha : soney chaandi (deenar, dirham yani rupey paise) key sath bhi ? unhoney kaha : nahin. aap ney to sirf zamin ki pedawar key iwaz deney sey mana farmaya tha. soney chaandi key iwaz to koi harj nahin. Sufiyan Sauri (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney bhi ye riwayat Rabeea sey bayan ki hai, lekin unhoney isey marfooa bayan nahin kiya. (lekin us ka koi nuqsan nahin hai kyonkey aksar logon ney isey marfooa bayan kiya hai.)"
3932,"Hazrat Hanzala bin Qais sey marwi hai, kehtey hain ke mainey Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey khaali zamin soney chaandi key iwaz thekey par deney key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : jayez hai. is mein koi harj nahin. manaa to tab hai jab zamin ki pedawar key hissey key iwaz di jaey. Yahya bin Saeed ney bhi ye riwayat Hanzala bin Qais sey bayan ki hai aur unhoney isey marfooa bayan kiya hai. jis tarah ke Imam Malik bin Anas (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney Rabeea sey marfooa bayan kiya hai."
3933,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apni zameenein bataai par deney sey mana farmaya. un dino soney chaandi key iwaz zamin deney ka riwaaj na tha balke aadmi apni zamin naalon key qarib ugney wali fasal aur moayan (tai-shuda) ghalley key iwaz bataai par deta tha, phir raawi ney puri hadees bayan ki. ye hadees Salim bin Abdullah bin umr ney Raafey bin Khadij sey bayan ki hai aur is hadees mein Imam Zohri par ikhtilaf kiya gaya hai. (Zohri key shagirdon ney ikhtilaf kiya hai. Zohri ki bayan karda riwayaat ko dekhney sey ye baat samajh mein aa jati hai.)"
3934,Hazrat Salim bin Abdullah ney bhi ye hadees isi tarah bayan farmaee hai. Aqeel bin Khalid ney is (Imam Malik) ki mutaabiat (pairwi) ki hai.
3935,"Hazrat Salim bin Abdullah sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) apni zamin bataai par detey they yahan tak ke unhein malum huwa ke Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bataai sey roktey hain. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr un sey miley aur kaha : aey ibne Khadij ! zamin ki bataai sey mutalliq aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kya bayan kartey hain? to Hazrat Raafey ney kaha : mainey apney do chchaon sey suna hai aur wo dono Badri sahabi they, wo apney ghar walon ko bata rahey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zamin kiraey par deney sey mana kiya hai jabkey main janta tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein zameenein bataai par di jati thin (aur aap mana nahin farmatey they). phir Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko khadsha (dar) mehsus huwa ke aisa na ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney is barey mein koi hukm jari farmaya ho magar mujhey pata na chala ho, is liye unhoney zamin bataai par deeni chhod di. Shuaib bin Abu-Hamza ney is riwayat ko mursal bayan kiya hai."
3936,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan farmatey hain ke merey do chacha jo Badri sahabi they, bayan farmatey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zamin kiraey par deney sey mana farmaya hai. (jis tarah Bishr bin Shuaib ney ye riwayat apney baap Shuaib sey bayan ki hai isi tarah) Usman bin Saeed ney (bhi) ye riwayat Shuaib sey bayan ki hai. lekin (bashar key bar-aks) us (Shoaib) ney Raafey bin Khadij key do chchaaon ka zikr nahin kiya."
3937,Hazrat Zohri sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne Musaiyab farmatey they ke soney chaandi key badley mein zamin kiraey par dena mana nahin lekin Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan farmatey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney is sey mana farmaya hai. (Imam Zohri key shagirdon mein sey) Abdul-Kareem bin Haris ney us (Shoaib bin Abu-Hamza) ki muwaafiqat mein is hadees ko mursal bayan kiya hai. (aur Shuaib ki tarah Abdul-Kareem ney bhi Imam Zohri aur Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) key darmiyan Hazrat Salim ka wasta zikr nahin kiya.)
3938,"Hazrat ibne-Shahab Zohri sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zamin kiraey par deney sey mana farmaya hai. ibne-Shahab (Imam Zohri ) ney kaha ke iskey baad Hazrat Raafey sey puchha gaya ke us daur mein log zamin kiraey par kaisey detey they? unhoney farmaya : ya to moayan (tai-shuda) ghalley key iwaz, ya ye shart lagatey they ke fasal pani key naalon key sath sath ya pani key mohgey key samney-samney ugeygi, wo hamari hogi. ye riwayat Naafey ney Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan ki hai aur is hadees mein Naafey par ikhtilaf kiya gaya hai."
3939,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko bataya ke merey chacha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaey. phir wapis aaye to unhoney bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zamin kiraey par deney sey mana farma diya hai. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr farmaney lagey : hum jantey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein zamin waala pani key naalon, jahan sey pani fasal ko lagta tha, key qarib ugney wali fasal key iwaz ya moayan (tai-shuda) todi waghera key iwaz bataai par deta tha. main nahin janta ke us (moayan todi) ki miqdaar kitni thi. (aur aap ney isi sey mana farmaya hai na ke aam bataai sey.) ye riwayat ibne Aun ney Hazrat Naafey sey bayan ki hai to unhoney  (عن بعض عمومتہ) key alfaz zikr kiye hain."
3940,"Hazrat Naafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) zamin ka kiraaya liya kartey they, phir unhen Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey koi riwayat pahunchi to unhoney mera haath pakda aur Hazrat Raafey key paas chaley gaey. main bhi unkey sath tha. Hazrat Raafey ney unhen apney kisi chacha key hawaley sey bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zamin kiraaey par deney sey mana farmaya hai, phir uskey baad Hazrat Abdullah ney kiraaya lena chhod diya."
3941,Hazrat Naafey sey manqul hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) zamin ka kiraaya liya kartey they yahan tak ke unhen Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ney apney kisi chacha sey bayan farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zamin ka kiraaya leney sey mana farmaya hai. uskey baad Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kiraaya lena chhod diya. ye riwayat Ayub ney bhi « Naafey an Raafey » ki sanad sey bayan ki hai lekin unhoney  عمومتہ  yani Hazrat Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) key chacha ka zikr nahin kya.
3942,"Hazrat Naafey sey marwi hai ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) apni zamin bataai par diya kartey they yahan tak ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilaafat key aakhiri dino mein in ko malum huwa ke Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) uskey mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey nahi bayan kartey hain, chunanche wo unkey paas gaey, main bhi unkey sath tha, aur un sey puchha to unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) zaminon key kiraaey sey mana farmatey they, is liye Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney uskey baad ye kaam chhod diya. phir jab un sey uskey mutalliq puchha jata tha to wo farmatey they ke Raafey bin Khadij kehtey hain ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney is sey mana farmaya tha. Ubedullah bin Umar, Kasir bin Farqad aur juweriya bin Asma ney us ( Ayub ) ki muwaafiqat ki hai."
3943,"Hazrat Naafey sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) zameenein kiraey par diya kartey they. unhen bataya gaya ke Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan kartey hain ke aap ney us sey mana farmaya hai. Hazrat Naafey ney kaha ke Hazrat ibne-Umar balaat mein unkey paas gaey. main bhi unkey sath tha. aap ney un sey (us key mutalliq ) puchha to unhoney kaha : han, waaqiatan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zaminon ka kiraaya leney sey mana farmaya hai, is liye Hazrat Abdullah ney zaminon ka kiraya lena chhod diya."
3944,"Hazrat Naafey sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko batlaya ke Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) zamin kiraey par deney key mutalliq eik hadees naqal farmatey hain. mein aur wo aadmi jisney aap ko ye bataya tha, aap key sath chaley yahan tak ke aap Hazrat Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaye to unhoney aap ko bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zamin kiraey par deney sey roka hai. uskey baad Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney zamin kiraey par dena chhod di."
3945,Hazrat Naafey sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zaminein kiraey par deney sey mana farmaya hai.
3946,Hazrat Naafey bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) apni zamin uski kuch pedawar key iwaz bataai par diya kartey they. in ko malum huwa ke Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) us sey roktey hain aur farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey mana farmaya hai. Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : hum to Raafey ko pehchanney sey bhi pehley zamin bataai par diya kartey they. phir unhoney apney dil mein shak sa mehsus kya aur merey kandhey par haath rakha yahan tak ke hum Hazrat Raafey key paas pahunch gaey. Hazrat Abdullah unhen kehney lagey : kya aap ney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko zamin bataai par deney sey mana farmatey suna hai? Hazrat Raafey ney farmaya : mainey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : zamin ko kisi bhi chiz key iwaz kiraey par na do.
3947,Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zamin kiraey par deney sey mana farmaya hai. is hadees ko Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kya hai. (aur Abdullah bin umr sey Amr bin Dinar bayan kartey hain) to Amr bin Dinar par ikhtilaf kya gaya hai.
3948,Hazrat Amr bin Dinar ney kaha : mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna ke hum zamin bataai par diya kartey they aur is mein koi harj nahin samajhtey they yahan tak ke Raafey bin Khadij ney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney bataai sey mana farmaya hai.
3949,"Hazrat Amr bin Dinar bayan kartey hain ke main gawahi deta hun ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna, jabkey un sey bataai key barey mein puchha gaya tha : hum is mein koi harj nahin samajhtey yahan tak ke Raafey bin Khadij ney hamen pehley saal batlaya ke unhoney Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko bataai sey mana farmatey suna hai. Hammad bin Zaid ney un dono (Sufiyan bin uena aur ibn juraij) ki muwaafiqat ki hai."
3950,"Hazrat Amr bin Dinar sey manqul hai ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna ke hum bataai mein koi harj nahin samajhtey they yahan tak ke (Yazid ya Hazrat ibn Zuber ki khilaafat ka) pehla saal huwa to Raafey kehney lagey ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey mana farmaya hai. Aarim ney us (Yahya bin Habib) ki mukhalifat ki hai aur kaha hai : « an Hammad , an Amr , an Jabir » ."
3951,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zamin kiraaya par deney sey mana farmaya hai. Muhammad bin Muslim taaifi ney us (Hammad bin Zaid) ki mutaabiat ki hai.
3952,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey mukhaahira, muhaaqla aur mazaabna sey mana farmaya. Sufiyan bin uena ney (dono sahaba ki) do hadeeson ko jama kar diya hai aur kaha hai : an ibne-Umar, o Jabir۔"
3953,Hazrat ibne-Umar aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney phal ki farokht sey mana farmaya hai yahan tak ke wo pak jaey. aur aap ney mukhaahira sey bhi mana farmaya hai ke zamin ko pedawar key tihai ya chothai hissey key iwaz bataai par diya jaey. usey Abul-Najaashi Ata bin Suheb ney riwayat kya hai aur us hadees mein is par ikhtilaf kya gaya hai.
3954,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey puchha : kya tum apni faaltu zameenein bataai par detey ho? mainey arz kya : ji han, aey Allah key Rasool ! hum unhen pedawar key chothai hissey ya chand wasq jo key iwaz bataai par detey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aisey na karo, khud kaasht karo ya kisi ko eik do saal key liye (aariyatan) bila moawza kaasht key liye dey do, warna rakhey rakho. Auzai ney us (Yahya bin abu-Kaseer) ki mukhalifat ki hai. aur us ney kaha hai : « an Raafey an Zuher bin Raafey » ."
3955,"Hazrat Raafey sey riwayat hai ke hamarey paas Hazrat Zuher bin Raafey aaye aur farmaya : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aisey kaam sey rok diya hai jo hamarey liye faeydemand tha. mainey kaha : wo kya ? wo farmaney lagey : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka farman hi sahih aur bar-haq hai. aap ney mujh sey puchha : tum apni ( zayed) zaminon ko kya kartey ho? mainey kaha : hum unhen pedawar key tihai ya chothai hissey aur chand wasq khajuron ya jo key iwaz bataai par detey hain. aap ney farmaya : tum aisey na karo, unhen khud kaasht karo ya kisi ko bila moawza kaasht key liye dey do ya isi tarah rehney do. ye riwayat Buker bin Abdullah bin Ashajj ney Usaid bin Raafey sey bayan ki hai to usey (Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij key bajaey ) Hazrat Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) key bhai ki riwayat banaya hai. (dekhiye, aainda riwayat)"
3956,(Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) key betey) Usaid sey riwayat hai ke (walid mohtaram) Raafey key bhai ney apni qom sey kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aaj eik aisi chiz sey rok diya hai jo tumharey liye faeydemand thi. wesay aap key hukm hi ki itaat ki jaeygi aur wohi sab sey behtar hai. aap ney zamin bataai par deney sey rok diya hai.
3957,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Hurmuz ney kaha : mainey Usaid bin Raafey bin Khadij Ansari ko ye zikr kartey suna ke unko muhaaqla sey rok diya gaya tha. aur muhaaqla sey murad ye hai ke zamin apni pedawar key kuch hissey key iwaz kaasht key liye dey di jaey. ye riwayat Esa bin Sahal bin Raafey ney bayan ki hai.
3958,"Hazrat Esa bin Sahal bin Raafey bin Khadij ney bayan kya ke main yatim tha aur apney dada mohtaram Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij key yahan parwarish pa raha tha. main baligh huwa to unkey sath Haj ko gaya. mera bhai Imran bin Sahal aaya aur kehney laga : abba jaan! hamney apni falan zamin do so dirham key iwaz kiraey par dey di hai. wo kehney lagey : beta ! usey chhod do, Allah Taala tumhen uski bajaey aur jagah sey rizq ata farmaeyga kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zamin kiraey par deney sey mana farmaya hai."
3959,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Allah Taala Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ko maaf farmaey, Allah ki qism ! is hadees (yani bataai sey mutalliqa hadees) ko main un sey ziyada janta hun. baat ye thi ke do aadmi (Malik zamin aur kisan) jhagad padey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar tumhara ye haal hai to zameenein kiraey par mat do. Hazrat Raafey ney sirf itni baat suni ke zameenein kiraey par mat do. abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) bayan kartey hain ke mazaariat ka maamla likhna us shart par ho ke beej aur deegar ikhrajat, zamin key Malik key zimmey hon aur kisan key liye pedawar ka chotha hissa ho."
3960,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Sirin farmatey they ke merey nazdik zamin muzaribat key maal ki tarah hai. jo kuch maal muzaribat mein durust hai, wo zamin mein bhi durust hai aur jo maal muzaribat mein durust nahin, wo zamin mein bhi durust nahin. aur wo is baat mein koi harj nahin samajhtey they ke zamin kisan key supurd kar dey aur wo is mein khud ya apni aulad aur apney sathiyon aur apney bailon waghera key sath kaam karey aur kharch kuch na karey balke kharch sab key sab Malik zamin ki taraf sey hon."
3961,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar key yahudiyon ko khaibar ki khajuren ( darkht ) aur zamin us shart par supurd kar di thin ke wo apney maal sey un darakhton aur zamin mein kaam kerengey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko kal pedawar ka nisf (bator Malik zameen) milega.
3962,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney khaibar key yahudiyon ko khaibar ki zamin aur khajuron key darkht us shart par diye they ke wo apney maalon key sath un mein kaam kerengey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko (bahaisiyat Malik honey key) us zamin ka nisf phal milega.
3963,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak mein zameenein kiraey par di jati thin. us shart par ke pani key naalon key qarib ugney wali fasal aur kuch moayan todi, na malum wo kitni hoti thi, Malik zamin ko milegi (aur baqi kisan ko )."
3964,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Aswad ney farmaya ke merey do chacha tihai ya chothai hissey key iwaz kaasht kya kartey they aur merey walid bhi unkey sath shareek hotey they aur Hazrat Alqama aur Aswad us baat ko jantey they lekin roktey nahin they.
3965,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke behtareen tareeq kaar ye hai ke tum mein sey koi shakhs apni (zayed) zamin soney chaandi ( raqam ) key iwaz thekey par dey dey.
3966,Hazrat Ibrahim Nakhai aur Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey manqul hai ke wo khaali zamin ko kiraey ( bataai ya thekey ) par deney mein koi harj nahin samajhtey they.
3967,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Sirin bayan kartey hain ke merey ilm key mutabiq Hazrat Qazi Shureh muzarib key barey mein do faisley farmatey they : kabhi to wo muzarib sey kehtey ke tujhey pahunchney wali musibat par koi gawah ya daleel pesh karo taake tumhen mazoor qarar diya jaey aur kabhi maal waley ko kehtey ke tum daleel aur gawah pesh karo jis key paas tum ney amanat rakhi hai, us ney khayanat ki hai warna us sey qism li jaeygi ke us ney tujh sey khayanat nahin ki."
3968,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab bayan kartey hain ke koi harj nahin ke saaf zamin soney chaandi ( naqad raqam ) key iwaz kiraey ( thekey ) par dey di jaey.
3969,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Badr key din mein , Ammaar aur Saad shareek bin gaey. Saad do qaidi laye, jabkey main aur Ammaar koi qaidi na la sakey."
